text: Laurent's long-tailed skink (Trachylepis raymondlaurenti) is a species of skink found in Angola, Democratic Republic of Congo, and Zambia. ==References== Category:Trachylepis Category:Reptiles described in 2019 Category:Taxa named by Mariana P. title: Trachylepis raymondlaurenti
